data.text:
Another example of why @GovRonDeSantis is right - all Covid "mitigation measures " are just theater. 

24 hours after this photo was taken I'm at magic kingdom where masks are required to ride the monorail. 

200 ppl crammed into a room is fine. 

8 people inside a rail car bad https://t.co/1gjLEA7zOV
@MisterCommodity What % of normal would u guess parks are at?
@MisterCommodity I had to wear a mask in that god forsaken room just two weeks ago!!!

Not a mask in sight. 

It's awesome to be normal
